parameters: There's a bonfire in a place like this...

You can fully recover your stamina by touching the bonfire.
There are no restrictions, so let's take a rest whenever our
stamina is depleted.

My heart feels a little at ease with the flickering of the
flames.... My stamina has fully recovered!

The flickering of the flames brought a sense of calm to my
heart.... My stamina has fully recovered!
How about over there? Have you found that Lunaroa?

If that's the case, she's not here. If you find her, either
she's already been killed or report it.

They're telling us to kill her, but... what are we supposed
to do, really? She's not someone we can handle...

We have no choice but to leave it to the higher-ups...
Fortunately, it seems that the principal from Magic Academy
is here this time.

That's reassuring, but... saying that it's impossible for us
alone to handle it is the same as...

\SE[14]I've taken it off! \SM[nod]\SE[13]There's no helping
it, be prepared...!
